{"word":"οἰκία","slug":"οἰκία","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>οἰϰία, ας, ἡ</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:οἰκέω\">οἰκέω</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> as structure<b> house <a href='B:470 2:11'>Mt 2:11</a></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ al.\">al.</a> Non-literal sense<b> <a href='B:500 14:2'>J 14:2</a>; <a href='B:540 5:1'>2 Cor 5:1</a>.</b> In<b> <a href='B:470 10:12'>Mt 10:12</a></b> <el>οἰ.</el> blends with<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> by metonymy, as group within a house <b>household, family <a href='B:470 12:25'>Mt 12:25</a>; <a href='B:480 3:25'>Mk 3:25</a>; <a href='B:500 4:53'>J 4:53</a>; <a href='B:530 16:15'>1 Cor 16:15</a>.</b> W. focus on entities rendering service <b><a href='B:570 4:22'>Phil 4:22</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:οἰκητήριον\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:οἰκιακός\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}